      <title>前谷歌員工稱因抗議以色列合約而解僱員工是非法的</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/ex-google-workers-say-firings-protesting-israel-contract-were-illegal-2024-04-30/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Alphabet 旗下谷歌的一群員工向美國勞工委員會提出申訴，聲稱該科技公司非法解雇了約 50 名員工，原因是抗議其與以色列政府簽訂的雲端合約。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/ex-google-workers-say-firings-protesting-israel-contract-were-illegal-2024-04-30/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 17:15:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
